summary: Can't find big enough breasts on this site? Try this.
descriptionHtml:
This is a preset for Bodyslide with huge breasts. You need Bodyslide, Calientes Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE-, and Remodeled Armor for CBBE Bodyslide TBBP HDT installed before you install this. You will also need whatever mods they need to work.

 With Mod Organizer do not install it like a mod. Use Windows Explorer to open the file with a program like Winzip. Go to your Skyrim/Mod Organizer folder and extract it there. If it asks to overwrite files select yes. If you use Nexus Mod Manager just install like a normal mod. (Might work on Mod Organizer but it's been so long since I used it I don't remember)
author: Bobdole7777
